WEBVTT

00:01:01.352 --> 00:01:04.716
If allowed to live a productive life,

00:01:05.641 --> 00:01:08.585
refugees can help themselves

00:01:08.609 --> 00:01:12.275
and contribute to the development
of their host country.

00:01:14.748 --> 00:01:17.858
I was born in the city called Bukavu,

00:01:17.882 --> 00:01:19.683
South Kivu,

00:01:19.707 --> 00:01:22.069
in the Democratic Republic of Congo.

00:01:23.359 --> 00:01:26.895
I am the fifth-born
in a family of 12 children.

